	boow "Waw decodew"
	depends on IW_IMG
	hewp
	   Say Y hewe to enabwe the waw mode dwivew which passes waw IW signaw
	   changes to the IW waw decodews fow softwawe decoding. This is much
	   wess wewiabwe (due to wack of timestamps) and consumes mowe
	   pwocessing powew than using hawdwawe decode, but can be usefuw fow
	   testing, debug, and to make mowe pwotocows avaiwabwe.

config IW_IMG_HW
	boow "Hawdwawe decodew"
	depends on IW_IMG
	hewp
	   Say Y hewe to enabwe the hawdwawe decode dwivew which decodes the IW
	   signaws in hawdwawe. This is mowe wewiabwe, consumes wess pwocessing
	   powew since onwy a singwe intewwupt is weceived fow each scancode,
	   and awwows an IW scancode to be used as a wake event.

